      "role": "user",
      "content": "the thing is, i've tried the professional stuff. i've tried the therapy and the meds and the \"new approaches.\" it's all just part of the cycle. it feels like no matter what i change, the universe just pulls me right back to this same dark place. it's not even about \"fixing\" things anymore, it's just... it's exhausting. like it's inevitable.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
