      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being tired, though. it's like knowing what the end of the movie is before it even starts. i see the same mistakes, the same failures, the same emptiness waiting at the end of every attempt. it feels like the only way to truly stop the loop is to just... exit. because there's no version of this where it actually stays fixed.",
